3.caption_en:
A 2x2 quadrant diagram mapping "Level of functional value" (horizontal) against "Level of vertical integration" (vertical), showing progression from digital products to a functionally integrated ecosystem; the top-right quadrant ("Functionally integrated ecosystem") is highlighted as the goal. Side bullet lists describe characteristics associated with higher vertical integration (strong connection, high context, openness) and higher functional value (high utility, high usability, increased value).

